</MudSimpleTable>

<br />
<br />

<MudGrid Spacing="4" Justify="Justify.SpaceEvenly">
    <MudItem xs="4">
        <MudText Typo="@Typo.h5">Earning Tokens</MudText>
        <br />
        <MudText Typo="@Typo.body1">
            Characters earn Reputation Tokens through:
            <br /><br />
            • Key story decisions<br />
            • Roleplaying aligned with specific aspects<br />
            • Completing quests or challenges related to aspects<br />
            • Character interactions and their outcomes<br />
            <br />
            The Guide awards tokens based on the significance and impact of the character's actions.
        </MudText>
    </MudItem>
    <MudItem xs="4">
        <MudText Typo="@Typo.h5">Spending Tokens</MudText>
        <br />
        <MudText Typo="@Typo.body1">
            Reputation Tokens can be spent in various ways.
            The players are encouraged to come up with creative uses for their tokens, and the Guide decides the effects based on what players want to achieve.
            <br /><br />
            • Influencing other characters to sway decisions or gain favors<br />
            • Enhance related skills temporarily<br />
            • Gain social advantage in relevant interactions<br />
            • Trade for various resources or gear<br />
            • Improve relationships with factions and organizations<br />
            • Call for divine intervention from a higher power<br />
        </MudText>
    </MudItem>
</MudGrid>

